Community Bank", "bbox": [104.2, 811.1, 319.5, 834.4]}, {"text": "Key Community Bank serves individuals and small to mid-sized businesses through its 15-state branch network.", "bbox": [104.2, 861.1, 1135.9, 884.4]}, {"text": "Individuals are provided branch-based deposit and investment products, personal finance services, and loans,", "bbox": [104.2, 911.1, 1123.2, 934.4]}, {"text": "including residential mortgages, home equity, credit card, and various types of installment loans. Key Community", "bbox": [104.2, 936.1, 1147.1, 959.4]}, {"text": "Bank also purchases retail auto sales contracts via a network of auto dealerships.  The auto dealerships finance the", "bbox": [104.2, 961.1, 1175.0, 984.4]}, {"text": "sale of automobiles as the initial lender and then assign the contracts to us pursuant to dealer agreements. In", "bbox": [104.2, 986.1, 1116.3, 1009.4]}, {"text": "addition, financial, estate and retirement planning, asset management services, and Delaware Trust capabilities are", "bbox": [104.2, 1011.1, 1171.9, 1034.4]}, {"text": "offered to assist high-net-worth clients with their banking, trust, portfolio management, life insurance, charitable", "bbox": [104.2, 1036.1, 1129.7, 1059.4]}, {"text": "giving, and related needs.", "bbox": [104.2, 1061.1, 342.7, 1084.4]}, {"text": "Small businesses are provided deposit, investment and credit products, and business advisory services. Mid-sized", "bbox": [104.2, 1111.1, 1162.4, 1134.4]}, {"text": "businesses are provided products and services, some of which are delivered by Key Corporate Bank, that include", "bbox": [104.2, 1136.1, 1154.4, 1159.4]}, {"text": "commercial lending, cash management, equipment leasing, investment, and employee benefit programs,", "bbox": [104.2, 1161.1, 1075.6, 1184.4]}, {"text": "succession planning, access to capital markets, derivatives, and foreign exchange.", "bbox": [104.2, 1186.1, 866.1, 1209.4]}, {"text": "Key Corporate Bank", "bbox": [104.2, 1236.1, 304.4, 1259.4]}, {"text": "Key Corporate Bank is a full-service corporate and investment bank focused principally on serving the needs of", "bbox": [104.2, 1286.1, 1132.4, 1309.4]}, {"text": "middle market clients in seven industry sectors: consumer, energy, healthcare, industrial, public sector, real estate,", "bbox": [104.2, 1311.1, 1162.1, 1334.4]}, {"text": "and technology. Key Corporate Bank delivers a broad suite of banking and capital markets products to its clients,", "bbox": [104.2, 1336.1, 1147.1, 1359.4]}, {"text": "including syndicated finance, debt and equity capital markets, commercial payments, equipment finance,", "bbox": [104.2, 1361.1, 1072.2, 1384.4]}, {"text": "commercial mortgage banking, derivatives, foreign exchange, financial advisory, and public finance. Key Corporate", "bbox": [104.2, 1386.1, 1166.8, 1409.4]}, {"text": "Bank is also a significant servicer of commercial mortgage loans and a significant special servicer of CMBS. Key", "bbox": [104.2, 1411.1, 1143.9, 1434.4]}, {"text": "Corporate Bank delivers many of its product capabilities to clients of Key Community Bank.", "bbox": [104.2, 1436.1, 941.3, 1459.4]}, {"text": "Other Segments", "bbox": [104.2, 1486.1, 265.1, 1509.4]}, {"text": "Other Segments consists of Corporate Treasury, Principal Investing, and various exit portfolios.", "bbox": [104.2, 1536.1, 978.0, 1559.4]}]}